OL,3,CDisgraced police chief who lied about
OL,4,Cmilitary service wore NI Troubles medal
OL,6,FA Northern Ireland army veteran says a
OL,7,Fsacked chief constable who fabricated
OL,8,Fa military career wearing medals he
OL,9,Fwas never awarded - including one for
OL,10,Fservice during the Troubles ` should
OL,11,Ffeel the full weight of the law.
OL,13,FThe scandal has prompted a move by the
OL,14,FNI Policing Board to review its
OL,15,Fvetting procedures.
OL,17,FLast week Nick Adderley, who headed up
OL,18,FNorthamptonshire police force, was
OL,19,Fdismissed for gross misconduct over a
OL,20,Fjaw-dropping web of lies that
OL,21,Feventually caught up with him.
