OL,6,FIt is given to those who served in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland during the Troubles `
OL,8,Fhundreds were killed.
OL,10,FGraham Eve has lost many friends and
OL,11,Fwas there in the aftermath of the
OL,12,FNarrow Water atrocity when 18 soldiers
OL,13,Fwere killed in August 1979 at the
OL,14,Fhands of the IRA.
OL,16,FHe has branded Adderley's 'stolen
OL,17,Fvalour' disgusting.
