OL,6,F"It's all about my friends who I lost,
OL,7,Fgood friends. We went through training
OL,8,Ftogether, we went through a lot
OL,9,Ftogether," said Graham Eve.
OL,11,F"When I wear these I will never forget.
OL,13,F"I hold him in complete contempt. The
OL,14,Ffact that he could have the audacity
OL,15,Fto wear those medals when I've lost so
OL,16,Fmany friends.
