OL,6,F"He should feel the full force of the
OL,7,Flaw that he was involved with as a
OL,8,Fchief constable and he should know why
OL,9,Fhe should feel the full force of the
OL,10,Flaw," Graham said.
OL,12,FAdderley's fall from grace brought to
OL,13,Fan end a policing career spanning 32
OL,14,Fyears.
