OL,6,FUTV attempted to contact him to see if
OL,7,Fhe wanted to say anything specifically
OL,8,Fto those who served in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, but we got no response.
OL,11,FIn a separate development, and on the
OL,12,Fback of concerns over how he got away
OL,13,Fwith this so long and managed to climb
OL,14,Fto the rank of chief constable, the
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board, which
OL,16,Fholds the PSNI to account, and also
OL,17,Fappoints senior police officers and
OL,18,Fcivilian equivalents, is reviewing
OL,19,Fvetting procedures in light of the
OL,20,Fscandal.
